{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Garbage Packer</strong><br>Step into the driver's seat of <strong>Garbage Packer</strong>, a <i>challenging physics-based garbage truck simulator</i>! Take control of a front-load garbage truck and master the art of trash collection and packing. With realistic controls and engaging gameplay, you\u2019ll experience the thrill and strategy behind managing your truck\u2019s load.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Physics-Based Controls</strong>: Operate the truck\u2019s arms to pick up dumpsters, dump garbage into the truck, and crush it with the packer for maximum space efficiency.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Clickable Buttons:</strong> The interior has two functional clickable buttons at the moment to increase Immersion.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/DumpGif-ezgif.com-speed.gif?t=1738525162\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic Packing</strong>: Carefully manage your truck\u2019s limited capacity by compacting and arranging garbage strategically to maximize your haul.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/PackerGif-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738525162\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Scoring System</strong>: Dump your load at the landfill and get scored based on how much garbage you\u2019ve collected and compacted. Can you out-pack the competition?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Views</strong>: Choose between first-person and third-person perspectives to experience the action from every angle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Leaderboards</strong>: Compete with players worldwide to see w